{"tid":677973,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊亞昆達替黑手黨工作或囚6年","createTime":"2018-05-25T16:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T11:55:33.000Z","uid":1121,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"96c06e5b7a2e06a5131530f0bf89a79a0ef94ecc","tid":677973,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=B3ifCGddofe07YKHAYxKP7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=deb66a33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前意大利國腳射手伊亞昆達因為替黑手黨工作，被警方拘捕，有機會被判入獄6年。<br />\n<br />\n意大利報章《米蘭體育報》指，意大利警方早前因為涉嫌為黑手黨工作，拘捕了147人，曾為意大利國家隊於2006年捧走世界盃的射手伊亞昆達（Vincenzo Iaquinta）亦是其中一人。<br />\n<br />\n伊亞昆達被指為意大利4大犯罪集團之一的Ndrangheta工作，包括窩藏手槍、放高利貸、敲詐、製造假賬單；據知，38歲的他在球員生涯尾段開始犯案。要是罪名成立，伊亞昆達有機會被判入獄6年，而其父親亦被捕，而且罪名更重，面臨19年牢獄生涯。<br />\n<br />\n伊亞昆達於烏甸尼斯成名，連續兩季轟入17球後，於2007年轉投祖雲達斯，2013年掛靴。這名高大射手曾為意大利上陣40次入6球，是2006年贏得世界盃冠軍的功臣，他於分組賽對加納入球。"},{"pid":"24c02de589907901fe159abc949c5665edea8f3b","tid":677973,"uid":61363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:03:32.000Z","msg":"好彩佢係足球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲糧應該夠佢過世"},{"pid":"57c7aaef46a0e9e5f13850ed6fb8de46cc129ac3","tid":677973,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"伊亞鳩達"},{"pid":"a0d4ca1e3d376dc279f5484b621beb1cdb6d6a6d","tid":677973,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"當年winning揾佢屈頭槌一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa6198ed92bd8ad74cafc0c8bad34eea402fab6","tid":677973,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"意假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a87fea5e571ba8779e8c2b0e1c23160b418554","tid":677973,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0d4ca1e3d376dc279f5